description: The man, aged in his 30s, was stabbed and killed in Kingswood on the outskirts of Dublin.
title: Kingswood, Dublin: Woman arrested after man fatally stabbed
title_page: Kingswood, Dublin: Woman arrested after man fatally stabbed - BBC News
maintext: The man, aged in his late 30s, was stabbed in the early hours of Tuesday morning in the Brownsbarn Estate in Kingswood, on the outskirts of Dublin.
